title: Tim Marquitz, ed. - Fading Light: An Anthology of the Monstrous
description: Fading Light: An Anthology of the Monstrous edited by Tim Marquitz retail epub Publisher: CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform (August 31, 2012) Language: English ISBN-10: 1479213489 ISBN-13: 978-1479213481 Fading Light collects 25 monstrous stories by authors new and experienced, in the genres of horror, science fiction, and fantasy, each bringing their own interpretation of what lurks in the dark.
